LA SANTA DIABOLIKA 2015 - 12ed. Genoa Tango Marathon Now Every summer in the month of july looking for “La Santa Diabolika” … in a very big terrace on the sea, we dance Tango Argentino three days all together. Where is possible eat, drink, swim, dance and enjoying of a beautiful site.
